Interview conducted by Martijn Arets:

"Sharetribes goal is to democratize the sharing economy. Their software makes it easy for anyone to create their own marketplace website without any programming knowledge. 

Last year they converted their traditional startup model into a steward ownership model. This model, which has been designed for companies with a purpose, prevents capital to be of extractive value of the company. In this video co-founder Juho explains their model and their motivations behind the decisions they made."

